<section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); line-height: 27.2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">为学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，厚植家国情怀，激发学生党员爱<span style="font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">国情、强国志、报国行，把爱国主义教育落细落实，深入贯彻落实习近平总书记关于科技创新和人才培养的重要指示精神，江西软件职业技术大学经济管理学院学生党支部于12月29日上午在A10-402会议室开展“大力弘扬民族精神，学好软件报效祖国”主题党日活动。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704795618419088964.jpg" title="1704795618419088964.jpg" alt="640 (1).jpg" width="665" height="492" style="width: 665px; height: 492px;"/></strong></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动一：奏唱国歌</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><section data-id="98902" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.3px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-flow: row;"><section data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 609.3px; line-height: 0;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 27.2px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 30.75px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;"><p style="margin: 10px 1px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2857em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动伊始，由党总支书记蔡平组织学生党支部全体党员同志奏唱国歌，全体人员原地肃立，激扬奋进的歌声鼓舞着现场的每一个人。</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 1px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动二：坚持“第一议题”</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-id="98902" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.3px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-flow: row;"><section data-width="100%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 609.3px; line-height: 0;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 27.2px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 20px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 30.75px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px;"><p style="margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">随后由党总支书记蔡平组织学生党员学习《习近平总书记关于青年学生成长成才重要论述摘编》以及《深入学习贯彻习近平总书记在文化传承发展座谈会上的重要讲话精神》。他表示必须深刻领会和全面把握习近平总书记从党和国家事业发展全局出发对广大青年提出的新要求、新希望，鼓励我院学生争做有理想、敢担当、能吃苦、肯奋斗的新时代好青年，坚持学习并弘扬中华优秀传统文化，坚定文化自信。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); line-height: 27.2px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 27.2px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动三：书记上党课</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><section data-id="98902" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.3px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-id="128838" data-color="#cd010a" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 546.925px; flex: 0 0 90%;"><section style="margin: 20px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.28571em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">他表示文化自信是一个国家、一个民族对自身历史和文化价值的清晰认知，文化兴则国运兴，文化强则民族强，我们唯有坚定文化自信，才能在世界文化激荡中站稳脚跟，必须把思想和行动统一到习近平总书记的重要讲话上，坚定文化自信，担当文化使命，扎实推进中华民族现代文明和社会主义文化强国建设，奋力谱写新时代中国特色社会主义新篇章。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动四：开展集中</strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">交流研讨</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p></section><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-id="98902" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.3px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 27.2px;"><p style="margin: 10px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学习之后，经济管理学院学生党支部全体党员开展专题交流研讨，学生党支部组织委员王艳萍、学生党员乐柯婧、熊路清参加此次研讨，紧紧围绕“深刻把握中华文明的突出性”、“深刻理解‘两个结合’的重大意义”、“更好担负起新的文化使命”这三个方面，结合自身实际情况，就如何有效地推动中华优秀传统文创造性转化、创新性发展，如何有力地推进中国特色社会主义文化建设，如何建设中华民族现代文明交流讨论。</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学生党员表示要坚定地做社会主义核心价值观的坚定信仰者、积极传播者、模范践行者，坚定文化自信、坚持守正创新、秉承开放包容的姿态、赓续历史文脉、谱写当代华章。</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 20px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学生党员还表示自己必将学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，坚持学习中华优秀传统文化，在日常生活中做到内化于心，外化于行。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动五：公示本月党费缴纳情况</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><section data-id="98902" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.3px;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-flow: row;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-style: solid; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-id="128838" data-color="#cd010a" data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 546.925px; flex: 0 0 90%;"><section style="margin: 20px auto 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.6em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">党费收缴作为党的基层组织的一项重要工作，是推进党建工作、保证党的活动正常运转的重要环节，在本次主题党日活动上，经济管理学院公示了本月党费缴纳情况，各党员都积极的配合党支部的工作并按时缴纳了党费，履行了党员义务。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></p><section data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 609.3px; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><section data-width="90%" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 90%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 609.3px; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); line-height: 27.2px; width: 677px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-id="122006" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 10px; height: 10px; background-color: rgb(255, 215, 133); overflow: hidden; transform: translate(-5px, 5px);"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(200, 12, 12); display: flex; align-items: flex-end;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 4px 0px 4px 15px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">结语</strong></span></section><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 1px; border-bottom: 15px solid rgb(255, 215, 133); border-left: 15px solid transparent; overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 2.43em; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">此次主题党日活动，进一步提高了学生党支部全体党员同志的政治素养，增强了党组织的凝聚力和战斗力，加深了学生党支部成员们对党的理论学习和传统了解，让学生党支部全体党员同志更加坚定了为党的事业贡献自己力量的决心。</span></p><section style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: unset; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0; height: 0px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><p style="margin: 0px 15px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.6em; text-indent: 0em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-shadow: none; font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240109/1704795695731011113.jpg" title="1704795695731011113.jpg" alt="640.jpg" width="549" height="297" style="width: 549px; height: 297px;"/></span></p></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>